[
  {
    "content_id": 694141,
    "reference_id": 13591,
    "title": "約翰二書 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "63001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>作長老的：有些譯本為了闡明文意而添加了<em>約翰</em>；約翰稱自己為<em>長老</em>以確認他在教會中的權柄。</p></li><li><p>寫信給蒙揀選的太太（希臘文kuria）和她的兒女：kuria可能是某個人的名字；但它更有可能是指某個特定的地方教會及其信徒（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:13\">1:13</a>）。</p></li><li><p>就是我誠心所愛的：這可能是指「真正的愛」（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:5-2John1:6\">1:5–6</a>），或更有可能是指那些同樣承認關於基督真理之人彼此的愛，以與假教師的謊言作出對比（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:7\">1:7</a>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:21-1John2:23\">約一2:21–23</a>）。約翰強調代名詞「我」，來對比那些拒絕真正的教會、沒有愛心的假教師。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "63001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:1",
          "end_ref": "63001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694137,
    "reference_id": 13587,
    "title": "約翰二書 1:1–3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "63001001-63001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>約翰以個人書信的規格開始書寫這封信。</p></li><li><p>約翰在這段簡短的介紹中提到四次真理，並在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:4\">一章4節</a>再次提到。約翰希望他的讀者了解並活出關於耶穌基督的真理以及他們與祂的關係，而不是被假教師誤導。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "63001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:1",
          "end_ref": "63001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694142,
    "reference_id": 13592,
    "title": "約翰二書 1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "63001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>基督徒的愛植根於認識真理。存在我們裏面的真理不只是事實或教義；它是神的同在（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15-John14:17\">約14:15–17</a>），祂會永遠與我們同在。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "63001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:2",
          "end_ref": "63001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694143,
    "reference_id": 13593,
    "title": "約翰二書 1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "63001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>恩惠、憐憫、平安是約翰確信那些活在真理和愛中的人會得到的祝福，且他們透過行動來顯明自己是神的兒女。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "63001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:3",
          "end_ref": "63001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694144,
    "reference_id": 13594,
    "title": "約翰二書 1:4–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "63001004-63001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約翰現在將他在引言中提到的真理和愛心（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:1-2John1:3\">1:1–3</a>）應用在讀者的處境中。活在真理和愛心中意味著要與真基督徒相交（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:4-2John1:6\">1:4–6</a>），但同時也要分辨假教師，不要聽從或幫助他們（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:7-2John1:11\">1:7–11</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "63001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:4",
          "end_ref": "63001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694145,
    "reference_id": 13595,
    "title": "約翰二書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "63001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>太太啊，我現在勸你：字面意思是<em>我勸你，女士。</em> 見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"13591\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">一章1節的研讀註釋</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "63001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:5",
          "end_ref": "63001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2JN 1:5"
        }
      ],
